column5: What are the best walleye lakes in the Calgary, Alberta area?

Depends what you are looking for,catch & release or keeping one for dinner.C&R lakes within 2hrs,Crawling Valley,Lake Newell,Kehoe,Pine Coullee.If you need dinner its Little Bow,Badger,and Buck(more than 2hrs),if you are lucky enough to draw Lake Newell you also can keep 2.Hope this helps.Chico.
